f93091d04475"],

Cell["\<\
Najpierw z menu \:201ePalety\[CloseCurlyDoubleQuote]  (Palettes menu) wybierz \
opcj\:0119 \:201eAsystent zaj\:0119\[CAcute]\[CloseCurlyDoubleQuote] \
(Classroom Assistant). Ustaw pulpit tak, aby paleta znajdowa\[LSlash]a si\
\:0119 obok okna programu Mathematica, ale nie nak\[LSlash]ada\[LSlash]a si\
\:0119 na nie.\
\>", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.407455184539785*^9, 3.407455288803026*^9}, {
   3.471209517101038*^9, 3.4712095588121233`*^9}, {3.471209602298024*^9, 
